    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Assess distal pulse, motor, and sensation\nXR\nAP view shows Salter-Harris III fracture\nLateral view shows Salter-Harris II fracture\nCT\nOften required to delineate degree of injury\nFracture involvement seen in all three planes",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Ortho consult in ED\nNonoperative\nUsually sufficient, indicated in <2 mm displacement\nOperative\nIf >2 mm displacement",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Disposition": {
